    rpg:artifactFormat "markdown" ;
    rpg:artifactLanguage "en" ;
    rpg:artifactText """# Health Pool — Damage Thresholds
- **0 to -5 (Hurt)**: Superficial injuries. Cannot spend on Investigative abilities. All Difficulties +1 (including Hit Thresholds). Medic can restore: 2 Health per Medic point spent (1:1 if self-treating).
